</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_443" id="220v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_443_r1l22">Hercʒog Otten von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_443_r1l23"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vns hat Reinhart von Hohenart genant frey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l24">neẅlıch <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef geſandt / daran er vns <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſacʒ aufſlagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l25">dauon vns niht wıſſend ıſt . Nu haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l26"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Frey </del> Reınhart <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıener ſey . Alſo <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_443_r1l27">wır ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> Petern Heydenaber <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıener </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_444" id="221r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l2">dem wir <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Reinharts brıefs ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> geben vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_444_r1l1">auch </ab></add> befolhen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l3"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu reden . vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l4">mıt fleıſſ . was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſachen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l5">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr gnade <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> / daʒ Jr Jn darinn <expan>gnedıklıche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l6"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> Jm des <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch <expan>günſtıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l7"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet / als etc das wellen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_444_r1l8"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_443" id="220v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog Otten von Peyern</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat Reinhart von
                                                Hohenart, genant Frey, newlich
                                                  <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief gesandt, daran
                                                er uns <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> sacz aufslagt,
                                                davon uns niht wissend ist. Nu haben wir
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Reinhart
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> diener sey,
                                                also <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> wir zu
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> Petern Heydenaber,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, <pb facs="#facs_444" id="221r"/>dem wir
                                                  <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> Reinharts briefs
                                                ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> geben und
                                                  <add>auch</add> befolhen
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden, und
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit fleiss,
                                                was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal in
                                                  <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir in darinn
                                                  <expan>gnedikliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>, im des
                                                  <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch
                                                  <expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc.
                                                Das wellen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
